psilon;&rho;&iota;&alpha;&rho;&chi;Î¯&alpha; &delta;&epsilon;&nu; &alpha;&pi;&alpha;&iota;&tau;&omicron;Ï&nu; &alpha;&pi;&omicron;&mu;ÏŒ&nu;&omega;&sigma;&eta;, &alpha;&pi;&alpha;&iota;&tau;&omicron;Ï&nu; ÏŒ&mu;&omega;&sigmaf; &delta;Î­&sigma;&mu;&epsilon;&upsilon;&sigma;&eta; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &omicron;&iota;&kappa;&omicron;&nu;&omicron;&mu;&iota;&kappa;Î­&sigmaf;, &kappa;&omicron;&iota;&nu;&omega;&nu;&iota;&kappa;Î­&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &omicron;&iota;&kappa;&omicron;&lambda;&omicron;&gamma;&iota;&kappa;Î­&sigmaf; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&tau;&epsilon;&rho;&alpha;&iota;ÏŒ&tau;&eta;&tau;&epsilon;&sigmaf;, &pi;&rho;Î¬&gamma;&mu;&alpha; &pi;&omicron;&upsilon; &sigma;&eta;&mu;&alpha;Î¯&nu;&epsilon;&iota; &kappa;&iota;&nu;&eta;&tau;&omicron;&pi;&omicron;Î¯&eta;&sigma;&eta; &epsilon;&gamma;&chi;ÏŽ&rho;&iota;&omega;&nu; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &pi;&epsilon;&rho;&iota;&phi;&epsilon;&rho;&epsilon;&iota;&alpha;&kappa;ÏŽ&nu; &pi;ÏŒ&rho;&omega;&nu; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &tau;&eta; &beta;&epsilon;&lambda;&tau;Î¯&omega;&sigma;&eta; &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &pi;&omicron;&iota;ÏŒ&tau;&eta;&tau;&alpha;&sigmaf; &zeta;&omega;Î®&sigmaf; &sigma;&tau;&eta;&nu; Î®&pi;&epsilon;&iota;&rho;&omicron;. &Alpha;&upsilon;&tau;ÏŒ &sigma;&eta;&mu;&alpha;Î¯&nu;&epsilon;&iota; &pi;&omega;&sigmaf; &tau;&alpha; &kappa;&rho;Î¬&tau;&eta; &pi;&rho;Î­&pi;&epsilon;&iota; &nu;&alpha; &gamma;Î¯&nu;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &pi;&iota;&omicron; &epsilon;&pi;&iota;&lambda;&epsilon;&kappa;&tau;&iota;&kappa;Î¬ ÏŒ&tau;&alpha;&nu; &pi;&rho;ÏŒ&kappa;&epsilon;&iota;&tau;&alpha;&iota; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &beta;&iota;&omicron;&mu;&eta;&chi;&alpha;&nu;Î¯&epsilon;&sigmaf; &Alpha;&Xi;&Epsilon; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&alpha;&nu;&alpha;&tau;&omicron;&lambda;&iota;&sigma;&mu;Î­&nu;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &sigma;&tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &epsilon;&xi;&alpha;&gamma;&omega;&gamma;Î­&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &sigma;&tau;&eta;&nu; &epsilon;&xi;ÏŒ&rho;&upsilon;&xi;&eta;. &Sigma;&eta;&mu;&alpha;Î¯&nu;&epsilon;&iota; &epsilon;&pi;Î¯&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &pi;&omega;&sigmaf; &pi;&rho;Î­&pi;&epsilon;&iota; &nu;&alpha; &delta;&omega;&theta;&epsilon;Î¯ &pi;&rho;&omicron;&tau;&epsilon;&rho;&alpha;&iota;ÏŒ&tau;&eta;&tau;&alpha; &sigma;&tau;&omicron;&nu; &omicron;&iota;&kappa;&omicron;&tau;&omicron;&upsilon;&rho;&iota;&sigma;&mu;ÏŒ, &tau;&eta;&nu; &pi;&omicron;&lambda;&iota;&tau;&iota;&sigma;&tau;&iota;&kappa;Î® &kappa;&lambda;&eta;&rho;&omicron;&nu;&omicron;&mu;&iota;Î¬ &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &tau;&omicron;&pi;&iota;&kappa;Î­&sigmaf; &beta;&iota;&omicron;&mu;&eta;&chi;&alpha;&nu;Î¯&epsilon;&sigmaf;.</p>\r\n<p>&Eta; &kappa;&iota;&nu;&eta;&tau;&omicron;&pi;&omicron;Î¯&eta;&sigma;&eta; &tau;&omega;&nu; &pi;ÏŒ&rho;&omega;&nu; &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &Alpha;&phi;&rho;&iota;&kappa;Î®&sigmaf; &xi;&epsilon;&kappa;&iota;&nu;Î¬ &mu;&epsilon; &delta;Î­&sigma;&mu;&epsilon;&upsilon;&sigma;&eta; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &pi;&omicron;&lambda;&iota;&tau;&iota;&kappa;Î­&sigmaf; &pi;&lambda;Î®&rho;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf; &alpha;&pi;&alpha;&sigma;&chi;ÏŒ&lambda;&eta;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; (&pi;&rho;ÏŒ&gamma;&rho;&alpha;&mu;&mu;&alpha; &epsilon;&gamma;&gamma;&upsilon;&eta;&mu;Î­&nu;&eta;&sigmaf; &epsilon;&rho;&gamma;&alpha;&sigma;Î¯&alpha;&sigmaf;), &upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&delta;&omicron;&mu;ÏŽ&nu; &delta;&eta;&mu;ÏŒ&sigma;&iota;&alpha;&sigmaf; &upsilon;&gamma;&epsilon;Î¯&alpha;&sigmaf;, &delta;&eta;&mu;ÏŒ&sigma;&iota;&alpha;&sigmaf; &epsilon;&kappa;&pi;&alpha;Î¯&delta;&epsilon;&upsilon;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf;, &beta;&iota;ÏŽ&sigma;&iota;&mu;&eta;&sigmaf; &gamma;&epsilon;&omega;&rho;&gamma;Î¯&alpha;&sigmaf;, &alpha;&nu;&alpha;&nu;&epsilon;ÏŽ&sigma;&iota;&mu;&omega;&nu; &pi;&eta;&gamma;ÏŽ&nu; &epsilon;&nu;Î­&rho;&gamma;&epsilon;&iota;&alpha;&sigmaf;, &beta;&iota;ÏŽ&sigma;&iota;&mu;&eta;&sigmaf; &delta;&iota;&alpha;&chi;&epsilon;Î¯&rho;&iota;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &phi;&upsilon;&sigma;&iota;&kappa;ÏŽ&nu; &pi;ÏŒ&rho;&omega;&nu; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &alpha;&sigma;&upsilon;&mu;&beta;Î¯&beta;&alpha;&sigma;&tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &alpha;&phi;&omicron;&sigma;Î¯&omega;&sigma;&eta;&sigmaf; &sigma;&tau;&eta;&nu; &epsilon;&nu;&delta;&upsilon;&nu;Î¬&mu;&omega;&sigma;&eta; &tau;&omega;&nu; &nu;Î­&omega;&nu; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &tau;&omega;&nu; &gamma;&upsilon;&nu;&alpha;&iota;&kappa;ÏŽ&nu; &mu;Î­&sigma;&omega; &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &sigma;&upsilon;&mu;&mu;&epsilon;&tau;&omicron;&chi;&iota;&kappa;Î®&sigmaf; &delta;&eta;&mu;&omicron;&kappa;&rho;&alpha;&tau;Î¯&alpha;&sigmaf;, &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &delta;&iota;&alpha;&phi;Î¬&nu;&epsilon;&iota;&alpha;&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &lambda;&omicron;&gamma;&omicron;&delta;&omicron;&sigma;Î¯&alpha;&sigmaf;. Î‰&rho;&theta;&epsilon; &eta; ÏŽ&rho;&alpha; &eta; &Alpha;&phi;&rho;&iota;&kappa;Î® &nu;&alpha; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&chi;&omega;&rho;Î®&sigma;&epsilon;&iota; &mu;&pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&tau;Î¬ &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &nu;&alpha; &epsilon;&pi;&iota;&delta;&iota;ÏŽ&xi;&epsilon;&iota; Î­&nu;&alpha; &kappa;&alpha;&lambda;Ï&tau;&epsilon;&rho;&omicron; &mu;Î­&lambda;&lambda;&omicron;&nu; &sigma;&tau;&omicron; &omicron;&pi;&omicron;Î¯&omicron; ÏŒ&lambda;&omicron;&iota; &omicron;&iota; Î¬&nu;&theta;&rho;&omega;&pi;&omicron;&iota; &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &mu;&pi;&omicron;&rho;&omicron;Ï&nu; &nu;&alpha; &epsilon;&upsilon;&eta;&mu;&epsilon;&rho;Î®&sigma;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &nu;&alpha; &alpha;&xi;&iota;&omicron;&pi;&omicron;&iota;Î®&sigma;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &pi;&lambda;Î®&rho;&omega;&sigmaf; &tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &delta;&upsilon;&nu;&alpha;&tau;ÏŒ&tau;&eta;&tau;Î­&sigmaf; &tau;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf;. &Alpha;&upsilon;&tau;ÏŒ &tau;&omicron; &mu;Î­&lambda;&lambda;&omicron;&nu; &epsilon;Î¯&nu;&alpha;&iota; &epsilon;&phi;&iota;&kappa;&tau;ÏŒ &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &xi;&epsilon;&kappa;&iota;&nu;Î¬ &mu;&epsilon; &tau;&eta;&nu; &alpha;&nu;Î¬&kappa;&tau;&eta;&sigma;&eta; &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &omicron;&iota;&kappa;&omicron;&nu;&omicron;&mu;&iota;&kappa;Î®&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &nu;&omicron;&mu;&iota;&sigma;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&iota;&kappa;Î®&sigmaf; &kappa;&upsilon;&rho;&iota;&alpha;&rho;&chi;Î¯&alpha;&sigmaf; &tau;&omega;&nu; &chi;&omega;&rho;ÏŽ&nu; &tau;&eta;&sigmaf; &eta;&pi;&epsilon;Î¯&rho;&omicron;&upsilon;.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&Upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&gamma;&rho;Î¬&phi;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; [1]:</p>\r\n<p>Fadhel Kaboub, &Pi;&alpha;&nu;&epsilon;&pi;&iota;&sigma;&tau;Î®&mu;&iota;&omicron; Denison, &Omicron;&chi;Î¬&iota;&omicron;, &Eta;&Pi;&Alpha;</p>\r\n<p>Ndongo Samba Sylla, &Nu;&tau;&alpha;&kappa;Î¬&rho;, &Sigma;&epsilon;&nu;&epsilon;&gamma;Î¬&lambda;&eta;</p>\r\n<p>Kai Koddenbrock, &Pi;&alpha;&nu;&epsilon;&pi;&iota;&sigma;&tau;Î®&mu;&iota;&omicron; Goethe, &Phi;&rho;&alpha;&nu;&kappa;&phi;&omicron;Ï&rho;&tau;&eta;, &Gamma;&epsilon;&rho;&mu;&alpha;&nu;Î¯&alpha;</p>\r\n<p>Ines Mahmoud, &Tau;Ï&nu;&iota;&delta;&alpha;, &Tau;&upsilon;&nu;&eta;&sigma;Î¯&alpha;</p>\r\n<p>Maha Ben Gadha, &Tau;Ï&nu;&iota;&delta;&alpha;, &Tau;&upsilon;&nu;&eta;&sigma;Î¯&alpha;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>[1] &Omicron;&iota; &alpha;&pi;ÏŒ&psi;&epsilon;&iota;&sigmaf; &pi;&omicron;&upsilon; &delta;&iota;&alpha;&tau;&upsilon;&pi;ÏŽ&nu;&omicron;&nu;&tau;&alpha;&iota; &sigma;&tau;&eta;&nu; &epsilon;&pi;&iota;&sigma;&tau;&omicron;&lambda;Î® &alpha;&pi;&omicron;&tau;&epsilon;&lambda;&omicron;Ï&nu; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&sigma;&omega;&pi;&iota;&kappa;Î­&sigmaf; &alpha;&pi;ÏŒ&psi;&epsilon;&iota;&sigmaf; &tau;&omega;&nu; &sigma;&upsilon;&gamma;&gamma;&rho;&alpha;&phi;Î­&omega;&nu; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; ÏŒ&chi;&iota; &epsilon;&kappa;&epsilon;Î¯&nu;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &tau;&omega;&nu; &epsilon;&rho;&gamma;&omicron;&delta;&omicron;&tau;ÏŽ&nu; &tau;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf; Î® Î¬&lambda;&lambda;&omega;&nu; &theta;&epsilon;&sigma;&mu;&iota;&kappa;ÏŽ&nu; &sigma;&upsilon;&nu;&epsilon;&rho;&gamma;&alpha;&sigma;&iota;ÏŽ&nu;.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '');
INSERT INTO `db_lang` VALUES (13, 'Hausa', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p><strong>BuÉ—aÉ—É—iyar wasiÆ™a: Zuwan Annobar Kwabid-19 ya sa dole sai Afirka ta zama mai dogaro da kai ta fuskar kuÉ—i da tattalin arziÆ™i</strong></p>\r\n<p>Kawo yanzu, ita Afirka dai ba ta sami wata mummuniyar illa ta É“angaren lafiyar al''umma ba bayan zuwan annobar Kwabid-19. To sai dai taÉ“arÉ“arewar tattalin da ya biyo baya ya bankaÉ—o irin koma-bayan tattalin arziÆ™in nahiyar da kuma gazawar tsare-tsaren gwamnatocinta.</p>\r\n<p>A matsayinta na nahiya mai arziÆ™i, Afirka za ta iya samar da ingantacciyar rayuwa ga dukkan mazaunanta. Afirka za ta iya samar da ababen more rayuwa da za su sami karÉ“uwa a duk duniya kamar na harÆ™ar lafiya da ilimi da kuma tabbacin aikin yi ga masu buÆ™ata gami da samar da tallafin hanyoyin kuÉ—in shiga ga waÉ—anda ba za su iya yin aiki ba. Shekaru gommai na sauka daga turbar nagartaccen tattalin arziÆ™i da zamantakewa na zamanin mulkin mallaka da na bayansa wanda janyewar wasu daga cikin Æ™a''idojin kasuwa ya ta''azzara ya tilasta wa Æ™asashen Afirka shiga wani mummunan yanayi wanda ya Æ™unshi gazawar tsare-tsaren gwamnati, mai alamomi kamar haka:</p>\r\n<p>. Æ˜arancin yalwar abinci</p>\r\n<p>. Rashin haÆ™o da sarrafa ma''adanai</p>\r\n<p>. Masana''antun sarrafa kayayyaki da na haqo ma''adanai marasa Æ™ima sosai.</p>\r\n<p>WaÉ—annan munanan alamomin guda uku sukan haifar da ci baya ga farashin musayar kuÉ—i na Afirka, wanda hakan na nufin farashi mai tsada na shigo da muhimman kayayyaki daga kasashen waje, kamar abinci da man fetir da wasu muhimman kayayyakin kiwon lafiya. Domin kare mutane daga wannan tashin farashin da aka shigo mana da shi, gwamnatocin Afirka sukan ranto kuÉ—i daga waje domin su Æ™arfafa kuÉ—aÉ—en Afirka kwatankwacin dalar Amurka da kuma Yuro.</p>\r\n<p>Wannan mafita da ake Æ™irÆ™irowa ta tilasta wa tattalin arziÆ™in Afirka shiga wani yanayi wanda kacokan yake maida hankali a kan samun Daloli ko Yuro domin biyan buqatar cin bashi daga Æ™etare. A dalilin haka ake É—ana wa tattalin arziqin Afirka tarkon É“arnar kuÉ—in da take da shi, wanda shi ne galibi ake É—abbaÆ™awa ta hanyar sharuÉ—É—an da Hukumar Lamuni ta Duniya (IMF) take shinfiÉ—awa da kuma yadda su ma sauran masu bin bashi kan matsa lamba domin kare muradunsu na siyasa da tattalin arziÆ™i wanda yake Æ™ara ta''azzara yalwar tattalin arziqi da ta kuÉ—i da ta siyasa a Æ™asashen Afirka. Qaidojin da hukumar IMF da sauran masu bada bashi kan gindaya sukan maida hankali ne a kan tsare-tsare guda biyar masu matsala kuma waÉ—anda ba sa biya wa Æ™asashen Afirka buÆ™atunsu, kamar haka:</p>\r\n<p>(1)&nbsp; HaÉ“aka fitar da kayayyaki</p>\r\n<p>(2) Janye wasu daga cikin Æ™a''idojin zuba jari daga Æ™etare</p>\r\n<p>(3) HaÉ“aka harÆ™ar yawon zuwa buÉ—e ido matuÆ™a</p>\r\n<p>(4) Sayar da kadarorin gwamnati</p>\r\n<p>(5) Janye wasu daga cikin Æ™a''idojin kasuwar hannayen jari</p>\r\n<p>Kowanne daga waÉ—annan tsare-tsaren tarko ne a lullube a matsayin mafitar tattalin arziqi. Habaka harkar fitar da kayayyaki waje kan Æ™ara adadin shigo da makamashi da injina masu tsada da kuma kayayyakinsu. Hakan ya kan Æ™arfafa Æ™wace filaye ko gonaki da sauran nau''ika na arziÆ™i, amma babu abinda yake Æ™arawa face fitar da kayayyakin da basu yi cikar Æ™ima ba. Babu shakka ba duka Æ™asashe masu tasowa ne za su iya bin irin wannan hanya a lokaci guda ba. Idan wasu Æ™asashe suna son cimma rarar kasuwanci dole sai da waÉ—anda suke shirye don yin kasuwancin a cikin yanayin da kayan da suke fitarwa bai kai darajar kayan da suke shigowa da su ba. HaÉ“aka zuba jari daga Æ™asar waje ya kan Æ™ara samar da damar shigo da ma''adanai sannan yana tilasta wa Æ™asashen Afirka shiga wata gagarumar gasa domin janyo hankalin masu zuba jari ta hanyar É—aga Æ™afa wajen biyan haraji da tallafi da raunana dokokin Æ™wadago da na muhalli. Sannan ya kan kawo sauyi a harkar kuÉ—i tare da komawar kuÉ—aÉ—e zuwa Æ™asashe masu Æ™arfi, wanda hakan yawanci ya kan faruwa ne ba bisa ka''ida ba. Bugu da qari, yawon buÉ—e ido ya kan haifar da Æ™aruwar shigo da ma''adanai da abinci a yayin da kuma ya kan gurÉ“ata muhalli da ruwa.</p>\r\n<p>Yawancin kadarorin gwamnati an siyar da su ne a a wajen shekarun 1990 (misali, kamfanonin sadarwa da na lantarki da na zirga-zirgar jirage da tashoshin jiragen sama dss.) Cigaba da sayar da kadarorin gwamnati zai qara ta''azzara tsarin tallafi ga talakawa da ya yi saura a Æ™arÆ™ashin kulawar gwamnati. Janye Æ™a''idojin hada-hadar hannun jari na buqatar sassauta Æ™ai''dojin harkokin kuÉ—i da rage harajin riba da janye tasarrufun gwamnati a kan jari da Æ™irÆ™irarren hauhawan farashin kuÉ—in ruwa da na musayar kuÉ—i. Duka waÉ—annan su ne su kan bada yanayin da yake jan hankalin masu zuba jari mafi girma a duniya. Za su shiga da kuÉ—insu don su siya da araha su sayar da tsada sannan su tsere su bar Æ™asa cikin Æ™unci.</p>\r\n<p>Daga Æ™arshe, duka waÉ—annan yarjeniyoyin sakar wa kasuwanci mara da manufar aiwatar da waÉ—annan matakai biyar, Æ™ara saka tattalin arziÆ™in Afirka suke yi cikin tasgaro. Wannan hanyar cigaban tattalin arziÆ™in mai É—auke da kura-kurai takan Æ™ara sa ''yan Afirka masu ilimi da qwarewar aiki tafiya ci-rani zuwa wasu nahiyoyi. A wasu lokutan, abin baÆ™in ciki ma shi ne, hakan yakan kasance ta sigar da tamkar suna gina wa kansu ramin mutuwa ne.</p>\r\n<p>WaÉ—annan tsare-tsare guda biyar da ake ganin za su iya kawo mafita (na wucin gadi) sukan kasance masu jan hankali saboda yadda sukan samar da sassauci da ba zai É—ore ba ta sigar samar da aikin yi, suna masu sawa a ji cewa ai zamanantarwa da kuma cigaban masana''antu ne. Amma fa a zahiri, samar da ayyukan yi É—in sun fi bada Æ™ofa ga Æ™alubale daga Æ™asashen Æ™etare da kuma rarraba kayyaki ko ayyuka ta hanyar wani tsari na duniya&nbsp; da jimillar duka buqatar duniya da abin da masana''antu suke samarwa ko kuma aikin da suke yi, da kuma farashin kayayyaki a duniya. Wato kenan, zai kasance za a ci gaba da sarrafa makomar tattalin arziÆ™in Afirka daga Æ™etare.</p>\r\n<p>Annobar Kwabid-19 ta bankaÉ—o tushen matsalolin tattalin arziÆ™in Afirka. Saboda haka, farfaÉ—owar tattalin arziÆ™i bayan annobar ba zai É—ore ba har sai an magance gazawar tsarin shugabanci wanda da ma can ake fama da shi tun kafin zuwan annobar. A dangane da haka, duba ga matsalolin yanayi da suke shirin faruwa da kuma buÆ™atar samun daidaituwa saboda matsalolin zamantakewar muhalli, dole tsarin tafiyar da tattalin arziÆ™i ya zama kan tsari tattare da hanyoyi daban-daban.</p>\r\n<p>Muna kira ga duka Æ™asashen Afirka da su samar da tsari mai alÆ™ibla wanda zai mayar da hankali a kan dawo musu da yalwar kuÉ—i da kuma na tattalin arziÆ™i wanda dole ya Æ™unshi yalwar abinci da ta makamashi da baya Æ™arewa da kuma tsarin gudanarwa na masana''antu da zai maida hankali a kan kayayyaki masu daraja sosai. Afirka dole ta kawo Æ™arshen nakasasshen tsarin ci gaban tattalin arziÆ™i da sunan gasa. Dole ne kasuwancin haÉ—in gwiwa a cikin nahiyar ya zamanto a kan zuba jari da aka shirya da juna da manufar haÉ—a alaÆ™a a fannoni masu muhimmanci sosai kamar harkar lafiya, da sufuri, da sadarwa, da bincike, da cigaba gami da kuma harkar ilimi.</p>\r\n<p>Muna qara yin kira ga ''yan kasuwa na haÉ—in gwiwa na Afirka da su yarda cewa akwai matsaloli a sha''anin haÆ™o ma''adanai, sannan su rungumi sabon tsarin haÉ—in kai da zai Æ™unshi musayar fasaha da kuma haÆ™iÆ™anin haÉ—in gwiwa a É“angaren bincike da cigaba da yalwataccen tsari&mdash;ciki harda yafe bashi&mdash;wanda zai kiyaye abin da ake samarwa da kuma aikin yi.</p>\r\n<p>Dole ne Æ™asashen Afirka su samar da bayyanannen buri mai dogon zango domin shawo kan Æ™alubale daga Æ™asashen Æ™etare. Yalwar tattalin arziÆ™i da ta kuÉ—i ba ta buÆ™atar a ware wani abu guda a yi shi; sai dai tana buÆ™atar yin wani abu da ya haÉ—a da tattalin arziÆ™i da zamantakewa da fifita lamarin muhalli, wanda ke nufin É—aukar arziÆ™in Æ™asa da kuma na nahiya domin haÉ“aka ingancin rayuwa a nahiyar. Wato kenan, hakan yana nufin zaÉ“en jarin Æ™asashen Æ™etare da za su zuba jari a cikin nutsuwa da kuma masana''antu masu fitar da kayayyaki da na haÆ™o ma''adanai.</p>\r\n<p>Tattaro arziÆ™in Afirka yana farawa da aiwatar da wani abu cikakken da ya shafi tsare-tsaren samar da ayyuka (shirin tabbatar da samar da aikin yi), kayayyakin harkar lafiya dana ilimin da gwamnati ke samarwa da harkar noma mai É—orewa da kuma makamashi da baya Æ™arewa da kuma tsayayyen tsarin adana makamashi da kuma jajirtaccen yunÆ™urin bunÆ™asa rayuwar matasa da mata ta hanyar damawa da kowa a harkokin dimokuraÉ—iyya, tare da baje komai a faifayi da kuma É—aukar É—awainiyar duk abin da ka iya faruwa. Lokaci ya yi da Afirka za ta ci gaba daga inda ta tsaya sannan ta yi muradin samun makoma mafi kyau wacce a cikinta duka ''ya''yanta za su murmure su kuma gano cikakkun damarmakinsu. Makomar da ake magana ba wani abu ne mai wuya ba, kuma za ta fara ne yayin da nahiyar ta tsaya da Æ™afarta a fannin tattalin arziÆ™i da na kuÉ—i.</p>\r\n<p>Wadanda suka saka hannu:<a href="#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1"><sup>[1]</sup></a></p>\r\n<p>Fadhel Kaboub, Jami&rsquo;ar Denison, Ohio, USA</p>\r\n<p>Ndongo Samba Sylla, Dakar, Senegal</p>\r\n<p>Kai Koddenbrock, Jami&rsquo;ar Goethe, Frankfurt, Germany</p>\r\n<p>Ines Mahmoud, Tunis, Tunisia</p>\r\n<p>Maha Ben Gadha, Tunis, Tunisia</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1">[1]</a> Sa hannun ya na wakiltar ra&rsquo;ayi na kashin kai na wadanda su ka yi rubutu ba na wadanda su ka dauke su ai ki ko kuma inda su ke wa aiki ba.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '');
