&nbsp;</p>', '');
INSERT INTO `db_lang` VALUES (22, 'Kipsigis - Kipsigis', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p><strong><u>Woluutietab Emotinwekab Afrika Kosupgei ak Miondo Nengoy ne bo COVID-19 Komagat Koweech Tononjinetabgei ne bo Magornateetab Emet ak Rabisiek: Baruetab Chitugul</u></strong></p>\r\n<p>Akoi inguni, kotom koiim missing miondo nengoy ne bo COVID-19 chametabgei ne bo Afrika; koik kityo keretab emotinwekyik nekoisib mionito kokokobor rorunet ak terterindab magornatosiekwyak. <strong>Kosupgei ak akwaiyeetab Afrika, emonitinwekyik kotinye kamuget kokochi sobet nemi barak </strong><strong>mengikwak tugul</strong><strong>.</strong> Emotinwekab Afrika komuchi kokoito toretet nebo emet neityin chitugul kou ribetab borwek ak somanet koboto kogeer kole kanyoor boisiet ne yae chi age tugul ne makyingei boisiet komakiutyen mokutiik chebo chemamuche kobois. Oot kounoton, ng''emetab bitonweek ak magornateetab pororiosiekab Afrika ne kigotestai kong''eete kotokobou kiplelaachek Afrika koboto ingoboigei emotinwechuto ak yateetab siroisiek, ko kikoyai emotinweekab Afrika kotebi en bananda ak rorunetab tugukab emet, ko u:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tononjinetabge ne momi eng&rsquo; amitwogik</li>\r\n<li>Tononjinetabge ne momi eng&rsquo; kimnotosiek</li>\r\n<li>''Factorisiek'' che chobe tuguk che bo aliet ne mi ngw''ony ak bolunetab maliik chekiibe koba emotinwekab sang</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Tuguchuto (makararon) somokko kikochilji ng&rsquo;wony missing alietab rabisiekab chebo emotinweekab Afrika, ne igochin koba barak alietab tugukab emotinweekab sang'' che u amitwogik, mwanik ak tugukab kanyaiseet. Asikomuch Afrika koriib aliet ab tuguk komaba barak kotienge ak tugukab sang chemi alienywa barak, serikalisiekab Afrika koyaache kobeseen rabinishek ab sang asikokimiit rabishek chwak ingekerchin ak chebo Amerika ak Ulaya.Orani maititayat kokikoyai bandaptai chebo Afrika kotitiryenchi en orogenet aletab dollars ana ko euros sikeyaktaen besendo nebo sang. Chenganibo dollars ak euros kokikotokyi magornatosiekab Afrika kokichak kou elemokto kipagengeisiekab ribetab magornatosiekab ngwony kou IMF ak korik alak chebesendo rabishek. Kipangengeisiek chuto tugul komoche koriib makutiikwak chebo bolatet ak magornatosiekwak ngandan ribonito tinye kipangengeisiekchebo sang ko kikong&rsquo;em tonoonjitabge nebo Afrika eng magornatosiek, rabishek ak bolatet. Ng''atutiik che tile kipagengeitab IMF ak kipangengeisiek chebo besendo kotakyinke oratinwek mut che ng&rsquo;eme bandaptai kotugul:</p>\r\n<p>Oretinwechuton ko:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>iyotetab magornateet kobun koyoktoitab tuguk koba emotinwekab sang</li>\r\n<li>yatetab emet asikobwa rabishekab sang</li>\r\n<li>Mageetab mung''areetab rutoiyweek</li>\r\n<li>Aldaetab kampunisiek ab poror</li>\r\n<li>Yatetab indonyoisiekab rabishek</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>Oretinwechu tugul koratutiik chekimwoitoi kele kororon eng&rsquo; ribetab magornatoshiekab emet. Iyotetab magornateet kobun koyoktoitab tuguk koba emotinwekab sang kotese ibunetab kimnotosiek, mashinishek ak kebeberwek chebo factorisiek ak kochamda ibetab mbarenik ak maliik ng&rsquo;andan kiyoktoi koba emotinwekab sang tuguk chebo aliet nemingweny. Kounoton kora, matugul eng&rsquo; emotinwek chetokoloongugee cheimuche kosiib oranitobo bandaptai. Yon moche kosich emotinwek alak kimnotet nebo mungaret, koyaache komi alak che iyoni konget eng&rsquo; ngweny eng&rsquo; mungaret. Yatetab emet sikobwa rabishekab sang kotoreet iyotetab magornateet kotese ibunetab kimnotosiek ak kolasimisan emotinwekab Afrika kobos kelanutikwak kobun kostoetab aisurusiek, kachuchuchetab karametab boisionik choton, kostoetab ngatutiik cheribe kiboitiniik ak itondab emet. Kora koyae nito kotumdumok rabishekab emet ak ibetab maliik koba emotinwek chemogoreek, ko alak eng&rsquo; rabishek chuton kobo magendo. Takseet nebo kiprutoinik chesweitote kotese ibunetab kimnotosiek ak amitwagik kobun sang, cheyoe ngemsetab itondab emet kwo barak eng&rsquo; koristo neya ak beek chekiboisien.</p>\r\n<p>Kampunisiek chechang chebo poror ko kialda en kasarta nemoloo (cheu kapsimoisiek, sitimook, ndegeisiek ak alak). Ngotkotestai aldaetab kampunisiekab poror kongemokse kamugetab emet korib biik. Yatetab indonyoishiekab rabishek komoche komokiriib ngalekab rabishek missing, bosetab aisurusiek, kostoetab ribsetab bandaptai ak kechamda nyorunetab keljin eng&rsquo; oret nenyumnyum missing ak ketii rabishekab emet ingekerchin ak rabinikab sang- tugul cheyoe komauit eng&rsquo; biik chemoche konyor keljin kobun rabinik eng&rsquo; oret nenyumnyumat missing eng&rsquo; ichek. Bichuto kobwone ak rabinik chebo chokchinet konyongwal eng&rsquo; aliet nemingw&rsquo;eny ak kwoldo eng&rsquo;alietab barak, asikomanda eng&rsquo; chokchinet ak kobakakta magornateetab emet eng&rsquo; sinet.</p>\r\n<p>Nebo let, mung&rsquo;arosiek ak emotinwekab sang komokiriib makutiikab emet ak koyonchinosiek chebo bandaptai kotokyin kotes ak kokimiit oratinwek chukakemwa, cheyoe magornatosiekab Afrika koba eleya. Oratinwechu maititootin chebo bandaptai koyae komanda sang kipsomaninik eng&rsquo; bananda neisibu. Tokuneen bananito biik chebeku eng&rsquo; baarisiek ak oratinwekab meet eng&rsquo; biik chemokyinnge magornatosiek, chametaab borto ak itondab emet nekararan.</p>\r\n<p>Oratinwechutet mut chebo pong&rsquo;oonutiik komoite elekimokyinke ng&rsquo;andan kikecham kotienge ak keljinoik cheibu eng&rsquo; kasar nenwach kou boisionik ak yaetab emet kobur kou miten bandaptai ak chobetab tuguk chekimokyinge. Kounoton ine, eng&rsquo; imanit, boisionik chuton komotebiye kokoegee ako miten eng&rsquo; eleya ng&rsquo;otumdummok mungareetab ngw&rsquo;ony kotugul. Ing&rsquo;etil ngal, ko kokile tienge magornateetab Afrika maguutikab biikab sang.</p>\r\n<p>Mionibo COVID-19 kokokong&rsquo;any tikiitikab kaimutiikab emotinwekab Afrika. Kounoton, kebendi tai, komoimukoksei kowek emotinwek kotestai ak bandaptai eng&rsquo; oret nenyolu komakilitiit tuguk cheyoe kotebi emotinwechuton eng&rsquo; sinet. Kosupgei ak niton, koboto itondab emet newendi koyaitu ak mageet nebo waleetab emet ak sobet nebokila, pong&rsquo;oonutiik chebo magornateet komoche kisibeen oratinweek cheter.</p>\r\n<p>Kiguree emotinwekab Afrika tugul kochop oratinweek chetokyinge isunetab tononjinetabge eng&rsquo; rabishek ak magornatosiekwak, cheboto tononjinetabge en amitwogik, kimnotosiek chemobeku ak pong&rsquo;oonutiik chebo chobetab tuguk chemibarak aliosiekwak. Yoche kotonosi Afrika sindanetabke netokyin emotinwekyik bananda eng&rsquo; kainetab kindoen emet ingo eng&rsquo; toksetab rabinikab sang. Chorwonditab mungaret nebo emotinwek chebo komoswek cheterter en Afrika koyoche kobokotuiyetab pong&rsquo;oonutikab bandaptai cheoechindos ak komikotuyetabge eng&rsquo; komoswek cheu tililindab poror, looiset, ngalekab simoisiek, chigiletab bandaptai ak somanet.</p>\r\n<p>Kora keguree choronokab mungaret chebo Afrika koyan kole kikobuut bolunetab maliik ak maoret notet nebo bandaptai. Moche ichegeet kocham chorwandit nebo bandaptai netestoi ibunetab muswoknotet, chorwandit nebo imanit eng&rsquo; chiligetab bandaptai ak tononjitabge eng&rsquo; oratinwek cheimuch keboisien keriib magornateet ak boisionik</p>\r\n<p>Emotinwekab Afrika koyoche kochop pong&rsquo;oonutik chetononootin chebo koigeny cheimuch komobutok yan kotumdumok magornateetab ngw&rsquo;ony kotugul. Tononjinetabge nebo magornateet ak rabishek komomoche kitabaangee, ngandan moche keeret neyamat eng&rsquo; ngalekab magornateet, sobetab poror ak itondab emet. Ngalek chuton komoche kayumeetab magornatosiekab gaa ak chebo emotinwek chorubegee sikomukak sobet negaigai eng&rsquo; Afrika. Kounoton, komoche kegeer komie rabinikab sang chebwone emet koboto iyotetab magornateet kobun koyoktoitab tuguk koba emotinwekab sang ak bolunetab maliik. Kora komoche kinde tai mungaretab rutoiyweek cheribe itondab emet, iyotetab biikyok ak chopetab tuguk en ortinwekab keny.</p>\r\n<p>Kayumeet ab magornatosiekab Afrika konomen pong&rsquo;onuutik chetokyinge boisiosiek cheityin chitugul, tililindab poror, somanet nebo poror, temisiet nemoweche itondab emet, kimnotosiek chetililen chemobegu, ribetab magornatosiekab ngwony ak mageet newoo nebo ketoret neraniik ak kwonyik kobun kandoinatet nekararan. Inoni ko kasartab Afrika kwo tai ak komakyigee betusiek chekororon eng&rsquo; ele biik tugul koimuch konyor maguutikwak ak koyai boisiet neimuchi. Tai inito koimuch kenyor ako inomen Afrika koweek tononjitabge nebo magornateet ak rabishek.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><sup>1</sup>Baruani kotinye siyeetab:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Fadhel Kaboub, Denison University, Ohio, USA</p>\r\n<p>Ndongo Samba Sylla, Dakar, Senegal</p>\r\n<p>Kai Koddenbrock, Goethe University, Frankfurt, Germany</p>\r\n<p>Ines Mahmoud, Tunis, Tunisia</p>\r\n<p>Maha Ben Gadha, Tunis, Tunisia</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><sup>1</sup>Siyookab biichu koboru kobwotutikwak ichegen komotinyege ak chebo kipangengeisiek eleyoen boisiet icheget.</p>', '');
