»™i v&agrave; sinh th&aacute;itrong v&ugrave;ng v&agrave; pháº£i huy Ä‘á»™ng c&aacute;c lá»±c lÆ°á»£ng trong nÆ°á»›c v&agrave; khu vá»±c Ä‘á»ƒ cáº£i thiá»‡n cháº¥t lÆ°á»£ng cuá»™c sá»‘ng á»Ÿ to&agrave;n c&otilde;i lá»¥c Ä‘á»‹a. NhÆ° váº­y, c&aacute;c quá»‘c gia Phi Ch&acirc;u pháº£i ká»¹ lÆ°á»¡ng dá»±a v&agrave;o káº¿ hoáº¡ch chiáº¿n lÆ°á»£c d&agrave;i háº¡n cá»§a m&igrave;nh khi xem x&eacute;t, chá»n lá»±a hay cháº¥p nháº­n c&aacute;c chÆ°Æ¡ng tr&igrave;nh Ä‘áº§u tÆ° c&ocirc;ng nghiá»‡p xuáº¥t cáº£ng v&agrave; khai th&aacute;c ngoáº¡i quá»‘c. Káº¿ hoáº¡ch chiáº¿n lÆ°á»£c n&agrave;y pháº£i Ä‘áº·t Æ°u ti&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c chÆ°Æ¡ng trinh báº£o vá»‡ du lá»‹ch sinh th&aacute;i, di sáº£n vÄƒn h&oacute;a v&agrave; c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nghiá»‡p báº£n Ä‘á»‹a.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>ChÆ°Æ¡ng tr&igrave;nh huy Ä‘á»™ng c&aacute;c nguá»“n lá»±c cá»§a Phi Ch&acirc;u pháº£i báº¯t Ä‘áº§u báº±ng má»™t cam káº¿t thá»±c hiá»‡n ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch to&agrave;n dá»¥ng (chÆ°Æ¡ng tr&igrave;nh báº£o Ä‘áº£m viá»‡c l&agrave;m) táº¡o dá»±ng cÆ¡ sá»Ÿ háº¡ táº§ng y táº¿ gi&aacute;o dá»¥c c&ocirc;ng cá»™ng, khuyáº¿n kh&iacute;ch quáº£n l&yacute; n&ocirc;ng nghiá»‡p, nhi&ecirc;n liá»‡u v&agrave; t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n theo phÆ°Æ¡ng ph&aacute;p t&aacute;i táº¡o bá»n vá»¯ng. ChÆ°Æ¡ng tr&igrave;nh huy Ä‘á»™ng nguá»“n lá»±c n&agrave;y nháº¥t Ä‘á»‹nh pháº£i á»§ng há»™ v&agrave; cháº¥p nháº­n sá»± tham gia cá»§a giá»›i thanh ni&ecirc;n v&agrave; phá»¥ ná»¯ tr&ecirc;n tinh tháº§n d&acirc;n chá»§, minh báº¡ch v&agrave; tr&aacute;ch nhiá»‡m. Ä&atilde; Ä‘áº¿n l&uacute;c, Phi Ch&acirc;u c&oacute; thá»ƒ tiáº¿n l&ecirc;n v&agrave; nh&igrave;n vá» má»™t tÆ°Æ¡ng lai tá»‘t Ä‘áº¹p, trong Ä‘&oacute;, má»i cÆ° d&acirc;n Ä‘á»u c&oacute; thá»ƒ thá»±c hiá»‡n Ä‘áº§y Ä‘á»§ tiá»m nÄƒng cá»§a há». TÆ°Æ¡ng lai n&agrave;y Ä‘&atilde; c&oacute; thá»ƒ vá»›i Ä‘Æ°á»£c trong táº§m tay, v&agrave; sáº½ báº¯t Ä‘áº§u báº±ng viá»‡c gi&agrave;nh láº¡i chá»§ quyá»n kinh táº¿ t&agrave;i ch&aacute;nh.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>K&yacute; T&ecirc;n 1:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Fadhel Kaboub, Äáº¡i há»c Denison, Ohio, Hoa Ká»³</p>\r\n<p>Ndongo Samba Sylla, Dakar, Senegal</p>\r\n<p>Kai Koddenbrock, Äáº¡i há»c Goethe, Frankfurt, Äá»©c Quá»‘c</p>\r\n<p>Ines Mahmoud, Tunis, Tunisia</p>\r\n<p>Maha Ben Gadha, Tunis, Tunisia</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1.Chá»¯ k&yacute; thá»ƒ hiá»‡n &yacute; kiáº¿n c&aacute; nh&acirc;n cá»§a t&aacute;c giáº£; kh&ocirc;ng pháº£i &yacute; kiáº¿n cá»§a h&atilde;ng, nÆ¡i há» l&agrave;m viá»‡c hay c&aacute;c tá»• chá»©c c&oacute; li&ecirc;n há»‡ vá»›i t&aacute;c giáº£.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Äáº·ng Táº¥n Háº­u - <a href="mailto:hau.dang.tan@gmail.com">hau.dang.tan@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n<p>Nguy&ecirc;Ìƒn vÄƒn Tu&acirc;Ìn -<a href="mailto:nvtuan26@gmail.com">nvtuan26@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '');
INSERT INTO `db_lang` VALUES (43, 'Wolof', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '<p><strong>&Agrave;DDU BI AY KAANGAMI AFRIG &Agrave;DDU SI MBAS MI: JOTAAT SI SUNU KOOM-KOOM AK SUNU AM-AM</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Bataaxal j</strong><strong>&euml;m ci askan wi</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ba mbassum koronaawiris bi t&agrave;mbalee l&euml;mb&eacute;&nbsp; &agrave;ddinasi ba l&eacute;egi,Afrig daa melni kumucc ci ay loram. Waaye li feebar bif&euml;sal, mooykoomu sunu r&eacute;ew yi ne tekk. F&euml;sal naitdoyadi gi&ntilde;udoyadi si w&agrave;ll woowu ak njeexitall bi mu am si nekkinu askan wi.Moone de, Afrig&nbsp; war na m&euml;n a dundal ay doomam dund gu sell, ndax naat gi mu naat ak xeetu jumtuwaay yu bari yi mu &euml;mb.</p>\r\n<p>Si loolu, warna m&euml;na m&agrave;ttal jumtukaay yi &ntilde;u soxla, j&euml;mm&euml;lb&euml;r&euml;b u fajuwaay ak nj&agrave;ng ak nj&agrave;ngale yi &ntilde;u yitte woo. D&oacute;lli si, doomi Afrig war na &ntilde;u m&euml;na fejj seeni soxla, te ligg&eacute;ey warna leena y&oacute;mb. Ngir luni mel nak, askanu Afrig y&eacute;lloo nadund gu mucc ayip te yemb. Nguuryi aar leen te j&agrave;ppale ndaw &ntilde;i m&agrave;tta ligg&eacute;ey te neew doole.</p>\r\n<p>Ay atti att a ngi nii, ginnaw bi &ntilde;u moomee seen bopp, doomi Afrig di j&agrave;Å‹kooteel ak nootel, &ntilde;&agrave;kk ndax tinki -&ntilde;u duppee ko liberalizasion &eacute;konomig si nasaraan-bi leen t&euml;nk si ay bor yu dul jeex ak jafe-jafe yii nuy lim:</p>\r\n<p>-&ntilde;ak dessoo sa bopp si w&agrave;llu koom</p>\r\n<p>-tumuraanke si w&agrave;llu enersi</p>\r\n<p>-ak ay b&euml;r&euml;bu ligg&eacute;eyukaayyu doxatul</p>\r\n<p>Yokkute bii aju si IDE day g&euml;n at&euml;nk sunu r&eacute;ew yi si nj&euml;ndum enersi bi. Dey tax itam &ntilde;uy wuje ag kuje gu metti ngir jot allal jiiy juge bitimr&eacute;ew. Si kaw loolu, r&eacute;ew yu bari da &ntilde;oo yombal borom allal yi fi b&euml;gsanc: teggil leen yenn xeetu juuti yi, yolomal t&euml;r&euml;lini yoon si ligg&eacute;eyukaay yi ak si alam wi.</p>\r\n<p>Noo ko gisandoo, mbassumkoronaawiris bi dafa f&euml;sal jafe-jafeyu magyi r&eacute;ewi Afrig nekke si w&agrave;llu koom.Bu mbas mi weesoo, ba dem bi ak dikk bi t&agrave;mbaliwaat, nakka noonu njaay mi ak nj&euml;nd mi, wala si g&agrave;ttal nit &ntilde;i dellu si seeni yitt&eacute;, l&eacute;pp si anam yi g&euml;n;f&agrave;ww&ntilde;u jublu simatadi gi nu nekkewoon si f&agrave;nn yu bari, laata mbas mi di l&euml;mbee &agrave;ddinasi. Te muy law ba finuy bindee bataaxal bi. Ngir d&eacute;kkujafe-jafe yi nu d&euml;kmalsi alam gi ak ni ko askan wi nara dundee, soxla nanu politig si w&agrave;llu koom bu s&agrave;mmoo ak xalaat, doxalin aki t&euml;r&euml;lin yu bees.</p>\r\n<p>Jotna Afrig j&euml;m kanam, tesax askan wi namm na &euml;ll&euml;g bu mucc ayib boo xamne &ntilde;&euml;pp di na &ntilde;u si xeejj te m&euml;nal seen bopp. Boobu le &euml;l&euml;g m&euml;nees na&ntilde;u si jot. Mu ngi t&agrave;ambalee si Afrig moom boppam si w&agrave;llu koom ak xaalis.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>&Ntilde;i ko xaatim</strong><a href="#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1"><strong><sup>[1]</sup></strong></a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Fadhel Kaboub, Denison University, Ohio, USA (iniwersite Denison, Oxaayoo sa Etaazini)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Ndongo Samba Sylla, Dakar, S&eacute;n&eacute;gal (Ndakaaru si Senegal)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Kai Koddenbrock, Universit&eacute; Goethe, Francfort, Allemagne (iniwersite Goethe, Farankfoor sa Almaa&ntilde;)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Ines Mahmoud, Tunis, Tunisie (Tinis, sa Tinisi)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Maha Ben Gadha, Tunis, Tunisie (Tinis, sa Tinisi)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1"><sup>[1]</sup></a>Bataaxal bii mu ngi tukkee si &ntilde;i ko xaatim kott, li &ntilde;u si &agrave;ddu, jotewul dara ak fi &ntilde;uy ligg&eacute;eyee, wala &ntilde;ii &ntilde;uy ligg&eacute;eyal, wala mbootaay yi &ntilde;u bokk. Seeni kaddu ak xalaat i bopp la</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '');
